column5: Found this on the net what the heck is it? One ugly fish for sure!
thats a "Pinoceros" Half pike, Half rhinoceros
I dunno never seen anything much like it, it has ears like a hippo i dont understand.
WOW, that is one ugly fish. I would just cut the line, it could be contagious lol.
Looks like something I seem in a bar the other day
Probally a pike just caught somewhere near Dafasco
Looks like one of the Canadian Mosquitos.  Dang things bite hard.   (No offense my friends .. none intended)
Those are definetly hyppo ears, or a bad lapse in evolution...  Someone out there has a phrunky imagination and a lot of free time!  hahaah HD
